p: Based on the result of the local Moran's I autocorrelation ( Table 3), there were 31 high-high clusters and 3 high-low clusters in total at the county level through the five waves, with 12, 8, 2, 9 and 3 clusters in each wave, respectively. It should be noted that Anji county, Deqing county, Yuhang county, Xiaoshan county, Shangcheng county, Shaoxing county and Yuecheng county had long-term high-high clusters throughout the five waves (4,3,3,3,2,2,2 high-high clusters respectively).
